modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod fixes Blood Moon Trickle to increase zombie count on horde nights. Increases the number of zombies in the 4th wave from 1-2 to 50.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod fixes Blood Moon Trickle to increase zombie count on horde nights. This increases the number of zombies in the 4th wave from 1-2, to 50\. You should get [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) all night.

[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_BloodMoon_Trickle)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/), SphereII
